      "definition": "Ukuhlanganisa ngaphandle komthungo ukubhukha okusezingeni eliphezulu kwezokuvakasha nokusebenza kwe-e-commerce; ukuguqula izinhlelo zokubhuka zendawo eziqhekekile zibe yizinto ezihlanganisiwe, ezikusizindalwazi se-Shopify.",
      "etymology": "Kusuka ku-Afrikaans plek (indawo) + -ify (ukwenza noma ukubangela ukuthi kube), ngokoqobo \"ukwenza indawo ibekeke\" noma \"ukwenza indawo ibhukheke ku-Shopify.\"",
      "usage_heading": "Izibonelo Zokusetshenziswa:",
